The paper deals with the problem of recognizing freehand sketches, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves deep learning techniques, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of neural networks, which are often used in multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) applications.
